`Welcome Gimli son of Glóin! It is long indeed since we saw one of Durin'
`But the wearing is slow in Lórien,'
'Here is the city of the Galadhrim where dwell the Lord Celeborn and Galadriel the Lady of Lórien. But we cannot enter here, for the gates do not look northward. We must go round to the southern side, and the way is not short, for the city is great.'
'Hm, hoom!'
